headline: Is TE Connectivity (TEL) Pricing In Too Much Optimism After A 68% One Year Rally
summary: If you are wondering whether TE Connectivity's current share price reflects its underlying value, you are not alone. This article will walk through what that price tag really means for you. The stock last closed at US$241.01, with returns of 4.1% over 7 days, 8.2% over 30 days, 3.3% year to date, 68.0% over 1 year, 107.4% over 3 years, and 103.6% over 5 years. These figures raise fair questions about how much optimism is already built into the price. Recent coverage around TE Connectivity...
